<plot>Three women approaching 30 find themselves in varying degrees of unfortunate romance. The first (Ione Skye) still has emotional scars from her mother's long ago suicide and can't keep from noticing her photographer boy friend's (Steve Jones) not-too-furtive looks at his teen daughter's obviously nubile body. The second (Lumi Cavazos) has just been married 7 months and finds her husband (Steve Schub) is a credit card addict who quickly ruins their credit rating. The last (Amanda de Cadenet) is separated from her philandering husband (Barry Del Sherman) and is having a series of revengeful affairs that ultimately lead to a beating by one of her pick-ups.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?360029</url></doc>
